tly.\",\n  \"evidence_dir\": \"dev/plan/runs/A3-evidence/\",\n  \"log_path\": \"dev/plan/runs/A3-secondary-diagnostics-output.json\",\n  \"next_phase_recommendation\": \"Feeds A4 decision: THREADSAFE=1 confirmed (baseline for B.1 MULTITHREAD=2 target). mutex_atomic A.2 verdict corroborated by MUTEX_PTHREADS compile option. strace unavailable but not blocking — A.2 flamegraph evidence is sufficient. A.4 can proceed with: THREADSAFE=1 baseline, mutex_atomic dominant, canonical_lookup missing-index as secondary observation. B.1 should target sqlite3_config(SQLITE_CONFIG_MULTITHREAD) + potentially add write_cursor index on canonical_nodes.\"\n}\n","numLines":80,"startLine":1,"totalLines":80}}}
